author: cmiranda
title: WATCH: Turkey airstrikes strike IS positions in Syria
text: WATCH: Turkey airstrikes strike IS positions in Syria Associated Press / 07:26   The Turkish military carried out a number of airstrikes targeting alleged Islamic State (IS) group positions, shelters and vehicles in northern Syria. The military said Sundayâ€™s airstrikes and ground operations targeted 174 Islamic State group positions. ADVERTISEMENT Turkey claim they killed at least 42 Islamic State militants in the raids. Syrian government forces and Turkish-backed opposition fighters are in a race to seize the town of al-Bab from the Islamic State group. Turkey sent ground troops into northern Syria in August to support Syrian opposition forces in clearing a border area of IS militants and to prevent Syrian Kurds from making greater territorial advances.
